  "description": "Return true when the array is already sorted in non-decreasing order.",
  "solutionJava": "public static boolean isSortedAscending(List<Integer> numbers) {\n  for (int i = 1; i < numbers.size(); i += 1) {\n    if (numbers.get(i) < numbers.get(i - 1)) {\n      return false;\n    }\n  }\n  return true;\n}",
